Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.50,0:00:06.22,TD_Thoughts,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Like Ryuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.68,0:00:11.88,TD_Thoughts,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want it to work out between him and Minorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.88,0:00:14.01,TD_Thoughts,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.62,0:00:17.49,TD_Thoughts,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It hurts so much it's unbearable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.22,0:00:19.37,TD_Thoughts,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:28.35,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}TAIGA!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.21,0:00:33.51,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.87,0:00:35.55,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.82,0:00:38.00,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I-It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.81,0:00:40.65,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.65,0:00:45.06,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It must've been pretty traumatic for you when your friend, Aisaka-san, got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.93,0:00:50.17,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And now that you've awoken from your nightmare, Takasu-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.17,0:00:54.29,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please turn in that form by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.31,0:00:59.54,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm going to repeat it for everyone else, but please don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:00.49,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And your reply?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.74,0:01:02.24,TD_Main,Everyone,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.63,0:01:04.97,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:46.85,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In the end, the rescue team saved us, so we didn't have any real injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:51.11,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then Taiga's mother came to pick her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:54.50,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you keeping in touch?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.97,0:02:55.73,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kitamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:03:00.79,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sensei said that Aisaka isn't feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.79,0:03:03.12,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's staying with her parents to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.79,0:03:05.41,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Have you heard anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:06.66,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:08.82,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't reach her cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.82,0:03:09.75,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.47,0:03:12.50,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:15.86,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.86,0:03:16.82,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.75,0:03:20.64,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let everyone think that the one who went down to save Taiga was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:23.34,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If Taiga ever asks you, tell her that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:31.74,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tell her that she was unconscious the whole time and didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:32.94,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:38.82,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Does that have something to do with what Aisaka asked me on New Year's?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:42.60,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It does, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:48.73,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:53.17,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:55.24,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wanna go somewhere good?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.24,0:03:55.83,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Somewhere good?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.83,0:03:57.02,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:03:58.65,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's get some good food!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:00.92,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Get your mind off Taiga{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.29,0:04:04.09,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nothing, nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.99,0:04:07.23,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.23,0:04:09.56,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Haven't those guys before us been in there for too long?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:13.18,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu, you don't have to go home and make dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:15.88,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry we dragged you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:16.89,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.89,0:04:19.73,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We came all the way here, I can't just go home without trying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.46,0:04:22.93,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't wanna go home even after trying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.93,0:04:25.20,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When I think that I have to talk about my future with my parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:28.56,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You don't have to get that serious about it yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:32.15,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The survey this time is just to decide how to divide up the classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.15,0:04:34.67,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Notocchi's definitely going into liberal arts right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:35.43,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.43,0:04:37.53,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want to get into some liberal arts college.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:39.75,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then work at a publishing house as an editor for a music magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.97,0:04:41.44,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And then go independent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:45.09,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm fine with just graduating high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:49.06,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll probably end up helping my dad with his work, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:50.02,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.02,0:04:54.60,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No offense, but I'm surprised you guys are really thinking about your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:57.24,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:05:01.08,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you have to worry about? You're really smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:02.10,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're going into science, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.10,0:05:06.66,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You and Great Teacher Kitamura are more than good enough to pass the national exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:09.02,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I haven't even decided whether or not to go to college...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.02,0:05:11.45,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Next, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.39,0:05:13.95,TD_Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We finally got in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.34,0:05:17.88,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please have a seat anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.20,0:05:20.23,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So, how's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.23,0:05:22.21,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Have you checked up on her yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:23.02,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}On who?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.02,0:05:25.34,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kushieda, of course{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:27.55,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Liberal arts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:30.37,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}K-Kushieda!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:32.19,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:33.62,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I work here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:34.48,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What about softball?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:37.47,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Practice ends earlier in the winter because the days are shorter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:39.56,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just so you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:42.36,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you say, "A hot guy," I'll poke your eyes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:43.15,TD_Main,Each one of them,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A hot guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:43.71,TD_2nd,Each one of them,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A hot guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:44.53,TD_Main,Each one of them,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A hot guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.51,0:05:48.74,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry, three ramen bowls please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:49.71,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.71,0:05:51.15,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You have made a good decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.15,0:05:52.45,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Three ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:53.58,TD_Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:56.42,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You started yet another job?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:05:57.08,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:05:59.37,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The pay's good, so I thought I'd try it out for a couple hours each week.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:01.30,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why do you have to do that many{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:02.50,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.51,0:06:05.98,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Very soon the eyes will open...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.98,0:06:06.55,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The eyes will...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:08.02,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Open?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:14.89,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:23.86,TD_Main,Old man,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Endless circle of transmigration!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.24,0:06:23.86,TD_2nd,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait! That's dangerous! {jama: added}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:32.32,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:34.46,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:40.21,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She really never changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:41.71,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Next customer, please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:43.54,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you hadn't told us...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.94,0:06:47.22,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I never would've thought she had just rejected a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.73,0:06:52.49,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Really, women are hard to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.49,0:06:55.56,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Speaking of which, Notocchi, did you make up with Maya-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:06:58.47,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's still totally ignoring me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.47,0:06:59.35,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No surprise there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:02.31,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A girl's feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:16.83,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is she really not coming back just because she isn't feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.78,0:07:24.29,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Or is her mother selfish like that old man and won't let her come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:25.29,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:27.67,TD_FB,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.45,0:07:34.08,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Or did she figure out that I heard her...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:35.35,TD_FB,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Like Ryuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:41.81,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Career plan survey?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:47.19,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just write, "I will study hard, really hard!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:50.08,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even if I get into a national university that I can commute to from home...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.08,0:07:52.31,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just how much do you think it'll cost for four years?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.31,0:07:54.10,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It'll be fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:57.20,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't worry about the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:07:59.87,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Here, natto bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:01.91,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sticky, sticky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.09,0:08:05.86,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"Don't worry"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:06.68,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:10.46,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Unlike Yacchan, you're really smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:12.79,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}After getting the best education...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.79,0:08:14.93,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're going to get the best skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:19.24,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then you're going to go down the best, happiest path in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:21.20,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Isn't there some kind of saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:22.29,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How does it go...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:26.07,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you polish a gold stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.07,0:08:29.98,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The gold stone will really shine, or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:32.95,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"A jewel won't shine if you don't polish it."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:34.96,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's it degansu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.96,0:08:39.79,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryu-chan, you're all sparkly and shiny when you're studying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:44.50,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Looks like I've got to work and make about 50,000 a month...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:47.04,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No way, no working!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:48.78,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I still...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:53.31,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Working at Inage-san's place was an extra special exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:54.22,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You knew about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.77,0:08:58.60,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You won't be able to study if you start working.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:09:02.26,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And a parent and child eating a cold dinner separately...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.26,0:09:04.04,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's the point of living like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.04,0:09:06.10,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's not happiness at all{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:08.87,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because you keep saying, "Go to college, go to college!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:11.34,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.34,0:09:13.49,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It'll all work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:19.83,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:22.52,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Always been like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.52,0:09:23.70,TD_FB,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.15,0:09:28.21,TD_FB,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just because you don't have a father doesn't mean you're worse off than any of the other kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:31.34,TD_FB,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because Yacchan is an amazing mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:36.26,TD_FB,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You'll always be perfectly happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:47.64,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Always perfectly happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.29,0:10:01.66,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you're worried about Taiga, she's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:09.89,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She always said she gets along pretty well with her real mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.39,0:10:14.97,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So I think she's probably having fun hanging out with her mom after such a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.97,0:10:17.34,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:18.80,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, Kushieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.79,0:10:20.77,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu, you're here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:24.61,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're here for the club budget?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.61,0:10:26.74,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry! I'll turn it in later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.74,0:10:29.24,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, don't forget, new team captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.24,0:10:30.90,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.11,0:10:34.66,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The new student council president is pretty busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.66,0:10:36.13,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}New team captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.13,0:10:38.74,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Weren't you already captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:42.69,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, Kitamura-kun's really busy with the student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.69,0:10:45.37,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So they combined the boys and the girls softball teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:48.70,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was appointed the new team captain of both.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:55.02,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Looks like I'm just unlucky. Soon, I'll be just as busy as Kitamura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:58.77,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}T-Then why did you take on another job?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.77,0:10:59.88,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Won't that make it worse?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.17,0:11:01.27,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:02.80,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Haven't you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.04,0:11:04.99,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"Work when you're young to rest when you're old."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:06.93,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But you won't be able to do either well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:08.27,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:11.48,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm working hard so I can do both well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:13.61,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:15.73,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Something you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.13,0:11:17.83,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"Something you can see"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:20.11,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's Amin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:23.04,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As lovely as ever.{You're as lovely as ever today.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.98,0:11:26.97,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kawashima, what's with that attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.97,0:11:28.10,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't come near me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:29.37,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You'll infect me with your stupidity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.59,0:11:31.89,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Isn't that great?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.89,0:11:35.03,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When the child's away, whatever the father does...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.99,0:11:38.83,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where're you going, Kawashima?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:43.25,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu-kun, this is where I say adieu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:44.80,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, class is going to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:02.77,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Skipping first period?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.77,0:12:04.79,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why is it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.52,0:12:06.69,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:09.41,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Listen... {jama: added}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.73,0:12:12.96,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's something I've been wanting to tell you for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.80,0:12:17.48,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}After blaming everything on me nonstop, there's still something left?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.48,0:12:20.34,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That space you're sitting in is actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:22.63,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}HAUNTED!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.46,0:12:25.43,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}S-Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:28.31,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Between those vending machines...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.83,0:12:32.02,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A lonely girl who failed in love, in one fell swoop...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:33.77,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why didn't you say so earlier?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:37.15,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But nothing's happened, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:42.60,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think ghosts have personalities too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.60,0:12:48.08,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They only appear in front of people who they want to see and understand them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:49.78,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:51.87,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I saw a ghost too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:53.13,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:13:01.17,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want to get lost in longing for something I can't see and lose the things I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:01.84,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:04.22,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Who cares.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:05.52,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want to hear the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.52,0:13:07.97,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You'll understand if you hear the rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.77,0:13:10.13,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.13,0:13:12.65,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You just to want say that if I had just kept quietly watching until the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.65,0:13:16.77,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I hadn't said something unnecessary and messed it all up, it would've come out alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:19.11,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nevermind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:21.70,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Talking to you makes me feel like I'm on my period.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.70,0:13:23.97,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I won't waver anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:26.80,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll face forward and chase after what I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:28.37,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, just shut up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:29.75,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I won't waver!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:30.74,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:31.53,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll decide by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:34.29,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Everything! Properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:37.82,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:43.63,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}About your career plans...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.07,0:13:45.09,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:47.21,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I haven't reached an agreement with my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.21,0:13:53.64,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then do you still feel the same about what you wrote at the beginning of the school year?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:55.89,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:58.68,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu-kun, you're a really good student.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.68,0:14:03.57,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As a teacher, the more I expect from you, the more I want to talk to you about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:06.93,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please don't expect so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.93,0:14:08.65,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My family's poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.65,0:14:11.26,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So the only problem is financial?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:12.49,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you're interested...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:13.69,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There are scholarships and educational loans{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.69,0:14:17.41,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is it so strange to choose not to go to college?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:21.01,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:24.88,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's just that I can't tell from this career survey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:29.33,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Not what someone else thinks, but what you, yourself, thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:32.29,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:39.69,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh? It's dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:42.06,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yasuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.35,0:14:44.32,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Still sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.97,0:14:52.12,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A job?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:54.81,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"It's alright."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:55.95,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"It'll all work out."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:57.12,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is what she meant?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.01,0:15:02.38,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I thought there wasn't any point to living if a parent and her child didn't have dinner together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:07.74,TD_FB,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryu-chan, you're all sparkly and shiny when you're studying!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.80,0:15:33.32,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How can I give it to her now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:36.66,TD_FB,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What part of a love letter is embarrassing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:39.44,TD_FB,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How about it? It's pretty sick, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.44,0:15:41.09,TD_FB,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't have the courage to tell her how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.09,0:15:43.56,TD_FB,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can only sit here and fantasize about what it'd be like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:44.92,TD_FB,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Of course, it's pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.45,0:15:47.40,TD_FB,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But even so, I don't think it's shameful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:48.51,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.51,0:15:51.88,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's not shameful to like someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.27,0:15:56.45,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.45,0:15:58.42,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Something like that to someone who likes me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.42,0:16:00.13,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even if I want to, I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.13,0:16:01.60,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She doesn't even answer her phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.87,0:16:03.41,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What should{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:05.44,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yasuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:09.68,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.68,0:16:11.22,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are you working more{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:17.91,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:20.20,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}TAIGA!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:23.16,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where were you and who were you with until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:26.40,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.40,0:16:30.71,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You idiot, pig, dog, beast, demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:33.26,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:35.48,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ouch! {jama: added}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:39.89,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:42.48,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You suddenly tried to strangle me and now you look at me weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:46.23,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was surprised because you just suddenly showed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.54,0:16:48.87,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You didn't even contact me once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.87,0:16:51.61,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was worried the whole{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:54.87,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I left my phone off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.87,0:16:55.96,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What the hell is with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:57.49,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Explain everything properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:17:00.99,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did you not come home because you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:06.27,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What was I going to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.27,0:17:07.08,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:09.23,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wasn't injured that badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.23,0:17:11.31,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The story about me being sick was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.31,0:17:12.30,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm completely fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:15.16,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I just wanted to skip school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:16.51,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:17.74,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Completely?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.74,0:17:18.82,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.94,0:17:23.14,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's been a while since I last saw my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.62,0:17:27.99,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We stayed at a hotel, went shopping, ate at restaurants, went to the movies, and other stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.99,0:17:29.94,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I totally let her spoil me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.63,0:17:31.57,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:34.06,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.71,0:17:37.28,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Didn't you say you wouldn't come into my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:39.46,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I lost my keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.46,0:17:42.05,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm going to get in through the window from your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.05,0:17:44.30,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Three second rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:46.00,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Can you get in within three seconds?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.24,0:17:47.71,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.18,0:17:49.94,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:51.34,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:54.21,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, since you're here, eat before you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:57.51,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's some natto left over, so I can just cut some onion and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:17:59.03,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm good, I ate before I came.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.03,0:18:01.68,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}T-That's right, Inko-chan wants to say hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.83,0:18:08.41,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Isn't he sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:09.86,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:11.32,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, this is "playing dead."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:12.65,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}One of his new tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.24,0:18:15.86,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did Ugly get a little fatter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:17.14,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.63,0:18:18.82,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Y-You think so too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:21.42,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's because he has no stress without you here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.42,0:18:24.52,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, I mean, he probably ate too much because he's lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:29.21,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He's as ugly as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.53,0:18:32.26,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Poke, poke, poke, poke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.26,0:18:34.19,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It really is nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.19,0:18:37.48,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This world with Taiga in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.95,0:18:41.13,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, Ryuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.02,0:18:44.95,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are you crying? That's gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.95,0:18:46.60,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm not crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:48.18,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was just yawning, yawning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.18,0:18:50.75,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, yeah, it is pretty late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:51.60,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bye, Ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.95,0:18:53.18,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.33,0:19:00.91,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:05.68,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is... I had some free time so I was cleaning out everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.68,0:19:07.70,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Remember, at the end of the year it was so busy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.48,0:19:07.70,TD_2nd,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:10.83,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm clumsy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:14.91,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I really got it after what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.78,0:19:16.30,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:19.55,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even a clumsy girl can be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:23.11,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was worried about it the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.86,0:19:27.22,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, did you ask Minorin about her real feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:29.00,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:30.31,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:35.39,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because of the big mess I caused, you couldn't ask her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.39,0:19:37.63,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why is she worrying about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.39,0:19:38.94,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I won't be clumsy anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:38.96,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even though...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.45,0:19:40.64,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.64,0:19:41.94,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It'll be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.72,0:19:44.09,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It'll be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.15,0:19:48.49,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sure it'll work out between you and Minorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:54.03,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.69,0:20:02.93,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, Ryuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:06.11,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't just stand there, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:11.42,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.42,0:20:13.27,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I always forget to lock it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:17.91,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A luxurious apartment with perfect security can be inconvenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:24.56,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:26.80,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, yeah, I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.77,0:20:28.89,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.13,0:20:34.83,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You went to look for me with Kitamura-kun and Minorin, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.19,0:20:37.88,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You don't remember, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:40.66,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Since you were unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.66,0:20:41.63,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.15,0:20:44.97,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I think I had a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.71,0:20:49.48,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kitamura-kun was carrying me piggyback.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:54.32,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I said something stupid to him, falling all to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.19,0:20:59.52,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That was a dream, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:02.67,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:05.15,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"Something stupid," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:09.62,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Does she want to act like it never happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.30,0:21:11.30,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.89,0:21:13.07,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.13,0:21:19.84,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But it is true that Kitamura climbed up carrying you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:21.74,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But you didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.74,0:21:24.85,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You were unconscious the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.85,0:21:26.09,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's what I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.57,0:21:28.08,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.08,0:21:29.75,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then I'm relieved! {jama: added}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.75,0:21:34.03,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was worried, "What if it was real?!" for a moment there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.03,0:21:34.93,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:36.90,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Alright! Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.90,0:21:38.48,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:39.15,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.06,0:21:43.48,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.48,0:21:45.43,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}One more time, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.06,0:21:50.87,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga, you're really...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:52.77,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.86,0:21:54.95,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Right? {jama: added}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.04,0:23:27.13,TD_Main,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thirty something rock, paper, scissors: scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.13,0:23:28.55,TD_Main,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yay, Yuri-chan won!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.55,0:23:29.52,TD_Main,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.52,0:23:31.80,TD_Main,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cho-co-late!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.13,0:23:35.09,TD_Main,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Valentine's fun!
